-- LG Elec shares jump to record, outlook strong
-- 
-- Wed May 14, 2008 9:41pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/15/us-lgelec-shares-idUSSEO29798020080515

 

 SEOUL  (Reuters) - Shares in LG Electronics Inc ( 066570.KS ) jumped nearly 6 percent early on Thursday, hitting its lifetime high, as a strong earnings outlook coupled with the won's recent weakness boosted demand for the stock. 

 By 0121 GMT (9:21 p.m. EDT), LG shares were trading up 4.84 percent at 162,500 won, outperforming the wider market's  .KS11  1.37 percent gain. The stock had earlier risen as much as 5.81 percent to hit a record high of 164,000 won. (Reporting by Rhee So-eui; Editing by Keiron Henderson)